These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, journalist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, davidoff
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold
House: victorian, gothic-revival
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the victorian house##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Job           | journalist | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | thriller   |
| Cigar   | davidoff  | dunhill     |
| Flower           | marigold       | zinnia     |
| House     | victorian     | gothic-revival        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, june
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, pink
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, german
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the person drinking water is the fan of pop##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the thai is on the left of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Birthday         | june | april |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Color           | pink        | blue    |
| Nationality     | thai  | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, pepper
City: prague, liverpool
2 different games are played: poker, scrabble
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, skateboard
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| City         | liverpool   | prague       |
| Game   | scrabble | poker |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | colombian    |
| Pet           | cat       | guinea-pig   |
| Transport         | skateboard   | ship     |

