2. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Birthday      | february        | september   |
| Color         | orange    | blue    |
| Food           | onion  | banana  |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | gospel     |
