2 different games are played: snooker, scrabble
2 different pets are kept: ferret, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, scooter
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | sprite      |
| Hobby          | collecting | cooking |
| Cigar           | oliveros     | tiparillo      |
| Game   | scrabble    | snooker       |
| Pet           | snake     | ferret      |
| Transport     | scooter   | bus         |

 